title: Sadyr Japarov - Wikipedia
snippet: Sadyr Nurgojo uulu Japarov (born 6 December 1968) is a Kyrgyz politician who has been serving as the sixth president of Kyrgyzstan since 28 January 2021. He previously served as the 22nd prime minister in the 2020 interim government, following the resignation of President Sooronbay Jeenbekov.

title: Kyrgyzstan: First lady’s prominence sets tongues wagging | Eurasianet
snippet: For nearly two decades, the wives of Kyrgyz leaders have largely shunned the spotlight. President Sadyr Japarov’s wife, Aigul, looks reluctant to follow suit.

title: Aigul Japarova - Wikipedia
snippet: Aigul Japarova (née Asanbaeva; born 14 November 1973) is the wife of President Sadyr Japarov and the incumbent First Lady of Kyrgyzstan; she is around five to six years his junior.
